      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six independent throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory-spec variable M differential lock. Mechanically flawless, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed to factory tolerances. The chassis remains incredibly rigid, retaining its factory-spec damping and bushings. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior exhibits zero clear-coat failure or rock chips, while the interior retains its original matte finish and tactile switchgear. A true purist\u2019s specimen with zero deferred maintenance.",
